# Read Project Agent Notes

Before editing this project, read `PROJECT_AGENT_NOTES.md` from the repository root.

Use that file for project-specific git rules, deployment notes, admin UI conventions, seating layout constraints, and other local context.

If the file is missing or cannot be read, mention that before making code changes.
